## **6. Technical Constraints (Non-Negotiable)**

|**Constraint**|**Detail**|
|---|---|
|**Local-First Preview Only**|NEVER introduce Sandpack, Vite, or external bundlers for the preview. The live preview uses a `srcdoc` iframe with a local Babel IPC transform. Tailwind/CSS is injected directly into the `srcdoc` string.|
|**No External Assets**|All images must be Base64 from `assets_cache`.|
|**Strict TypeScript**|No `any`. Interfaces required for all component props.|
|**Electron Security**|`sandbox: false` required for Vite preload ESM resolution.|

---

## **7. The Bridge Token Profile Schema (W3C DTCG Standard)**

Strictly enforces the W3C Design Tokens Community Group (DTCG) JSON schema.

Tokens must have `$value` and `$type`.

Supports **Modes** (Light/Dark) and **Collections** via SQLite composite unique constraints.

